struggled

00:25:23.919 --> 00:25:25.830
my whole life with everything I

00:25:25.840 --> 00:25:27.750
have,

00:25:27.760 --> 00:25:30.950
and I've sat at his feet wanting to

00:25:30.960 --> 00:25:34.470
