00:28:56.080 --> 00:28:59.350
'I give you grace every day just to do

00:28:59.360 --> 00:29:02.149
what you do to get out of bed.

00:29:02.159 --> 00:29:03.990
The moment you wake up and open your

00:29:04.000 --> 00:29:10.870
eyes, I've given you grace to do it.

00:29:10.880 --> 00:29:12.630
The very blood that flows through your

00:29:12.640 --> 00:29:14.870
veins,

00:29:14.880 --> 00:29:16.470
the thoughts that you think in your

00:29:16.480 --> 00:29:18.870
head...'When

00:29:18.880 --> 00:29:20.710
I hear him say those things,

00:29:20.720 --> 00:29:22.950
and I listen to him and hear his

00:29:22.960 --> 00:29:25.750
heartbeat...

00:29:25.760 --> 00:29:28.149
And all I'm asking you in these days

00:29:28.159 --> 00:29:34.149
ahead, Brandon, is touch not the glory.

00:29:34.159 --> 00:29:37.190
It's my

00:29:37.190 --> 00:29:37.200
trigger.'I

00:29:37.200 --> 00:29:40.389
said, 'You got it.

00:29:40.399 --> 00:29:48.149
Whatever it

00:29:48.159 --> 00:30:35.669
takes.'So

00:30:35.679 --> 00:30:41.029
I just caution

00:30:44.549 --> 00:30:44.559
you—if

00:30:47.360 --> 00:30:49.510
you can learn anything

